WEBVTT

01:34.680 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:47.680 --> 01:49.360
WUSHI NO.1 SENIOR HIGH SCHOOL

01:50.080 --> 01:51.400
See you, Dad.

01:51.920 --> 01:53.000
If there is anything you don't know,
just ask.

01:53.080 --> 01:55.160
- Okay!
- Your bag.

01:57.120 --> 01:58.560
- Bye.
- Bye.

01:59.560 --> 02:01.280
It's Class 17.

02:01.360 --> 02:02.840
- Okay!
- Make sure you go to the right class.

02:03.560 --> 02:05.520
Remember to drink water. Hot water.

02:20.760 --> 02:23.120
Senior. Can you please tell me
where Class 17 Year 10 is?

02:23.880 --> 02:24.880
Sorry, I just started school here.

02:26.520 --> 02:28.120
Go downstairs, turn left,
and enter the building.

02:31.480 --> 02:32.520
And?

02:33.040 --> 02:34.160
And?

02:34.760 --> 02:36.760
And check the classroom number
on the door yourself.

02:36.840 --> 02:37.920
Or do you expect me, your senior,

02:38.000 --> 02:39.160
to read them out one by one for you?

02:41.320 --> 02:42.640
My junior.

02:43.880 --> 02:44.720
Thank you, senior.

02:50.520 --> 02:51.440
Sorry.

03:03.800 --> 03:04.720
Excuse me!

03:07.520 --> 03:08.640
Sang Yan?

03:08.720 --> 03:09.720
I'm Wen Yifan.

03:11.160 --> 03:12.360
Oh, Wen Yifan.

03:14.240 --> 03:16.760
Everyone on the list showed up,
except you and Sang Yan. Sorry.

03:16.840 --> 03:19.600
Sang Yan sounds like a girl's name,
so I thought you were Sang Yan.

03:21.440 --> 03:22.280
Excuse me.

03:23.920 --> 03:25.800
- Sorry, sir. I came late.
- It's him?

03:25.880 --> 03:28.280
Late on your first day?

03:29.360 --> 03:30.200
Did you two come together?

03:30.280 --> 03:32.040
No, we didn't.

03:32.120 --> 03:33.200
I just couldn't find my way,

03:33.280 --> 03:34.600
and it took a while.

03:34.680 --> 03:36.360
What about you? What's your excuse?

03:39.440 --> 03:41.240
My dad didn't know
I was in high school now

03:41.320 --> 03:42.520
and sent me to junior high.

03:46.400 --> 03:48.480
Are you going in, Miss Sang Yan?

03:49.680 --> 03:51.360
I, the senior,
would like you to go in first,

03:52.280 --> 03:53.440
my junior from middle school.

04:02.320 --> 04:04.400
Take those two seats at the back. Go.

04:08.040 --> 04:10.920
That was the first time I saw him.

04:13.040 --> 04:14.160
When the teacher got our names wrong,

04:14.680 --> 04:16.000
I found myself momentarily lost,

04:16.079 --> 04:17.600
forgetting that he was Sang Yan

04:19.320 --> 04:20.360
and I was

04:20.440 --> 04:21.880
Wen Yifan.

04:21.959 --> 04:24.040
Alright, everyone is here.

04:24.120 --> 04:26.080
Now, we will proceed
according to student numbers…

04:26.160 --> 04:27.440
For a moment,

04:27.520 --> 04:29.440
it was like there was suddenly

04:30.040 --> 04:31.680
another me in this world.

04:53.320 --> 04:57.120
EIGHT YEARS LATER

05:01.200 --> 05:02.240
Dian.

05:03.720 --> 05:05.200
Qiao, all done with your work?

05:05.280 --> 05:07.240
Yep. Let's go. We'll party more later!

05:07.880 --> 05:09.480
You've been standing all night.
Aren't you tired?

05:09.560 --> 05:11.680
It's been ages
since we had a gathering like this.

05:11.760 --> 05:13.640
Surely we can't call it a night
just yet. Let's go!

05:13.720 --> 05:15.040
But I still have to go back

05:15.120 --> 05:16.400
- and organize my materials tonight.
- Don't forget the materials.

05:16.480 --> 05:18.720
Then I'll wait for you
to finish organizing your materials.

05:18.800 --> 05:21.920
I heard there's a New Year's event
at Overtime tonight.

05:25.000 --> 05:25.960
I'm already worn out
from working overtime,

05:26.040 --> 05:27.040
and now I have to go to Overtime?

05:27.120 --> 05:27.960
I'm definitely not going.

05:28.040 --> 05:30.920
- No way, you have to come with me.
- Yes way.

05:31.520 --> 05:33.080
- Please come with me. I'll wait for you.
- All right now.

05:33.160 --> 05:34.520
Be good and go by yourself.

05:34.600 --> 05:35.600
- I can wait for you.
- Come on.

05:35.680 --> 05:37.080
Just go. Don't wait for me.

05:37.600 --> 05:38.440
- Bye.
- Stay safe.

05:38.520 --> 05:40.160
Got it.

05:40.240 --> 05:42.480
Why didn't you go hang out
with your friend?

05:45.960 --> 05:46.800
Come here.

05:54.720 --> 05:55.600
Madam.

05:58.360 --> 05:59.920
We're done with work for today,

06:00.000 --> 06:01.520
and everyone did a great job.

06:02.040 --> 06:03.080
I think

06:03.160 --> 06:05.760
you really should take a break and unwind.

06:10.520 --> 06:11.600
Yifan,

06:12.720 --> 06:14.640
I feel like you're bottling up a lot.

06:18.160 --> 06:21.880
You should try to open up a little,

06:22.640 --> 06:24.400
let go of any negative emotions

06:24.480 --> 06:26.600
or unhappy thoughts,

06:26.680 --> 06:27.760
and welcome the new year

06:27.840 --> 06:29.720
with a fresh mindset.

06:48.400 --> 06:51.280
The new year will be good, right?

06:52.840 --> 06:54.920
- Happy New Year!
- Happy New Year!

07:28.640 --> 07:30.120
The new year

07:31.000 --> 07:32.080
will be good, right?

07:34.200 --> 07:35.880
Whether it's good or not

07:35.960 --> 07:37.720
is entirely up to you.

07:43.720 --> 07:46.480
MY NEW YEAR'S WISH

07:46.560 --> 07:51.080
MY NEW YEAR'S WISH
A PEACEFUL AND UNEVENTFUL YEAR

08:19.280 --> 08:20.800
Somebody just fell.

08:22.320 --> 08:24.160
Are you okay? Let me help you up.

08:27.320 --> 08:28.320
Sorry.

08:28.400 --> 08:29.560
You are…

08:30.080 --> 08:31.920
- Su… Haoan.
- Yifan.

08:34.200 --> 08:36.440
I'm not Wen Yifan. I'm Zhong Siqiao.

08:36.520 --> 08:38.039
How could you mix that up?

08:38.120 --> 08:40.559
Oh, that's right.
I meant you're Wen Yifan's friend,

08:41.080 --> 08:42.720
Zhong Siqiao, from the class next door.

08:54.840 --> 08:55.880
You are here.

08:56.800 --> 08:57.720
Who's that?

08:57.800 --> 08:59.120
He's my other business partner.

08:59.800 --> 09:01.520
You probably remember him.

09:01.600 --> 09:03.120
He was my classmate in high school.

09:06.360 --> 09:07.440
Headliner?

09:31.640 --> 09:34.800
Dian, do you know
who the Headliner of Gastropub Street is?

09:34.880 --> 09:36.760
It's Sang Yan.

09:37.280 --> 09:40.240
Did you not recognize him,
or were you just not telling me?

09:44.160 --> 09:45.960
SANG YAN

09:46.040 --> 09:48.960
HAPPY NEW YEAR!
YOU DON'T HAVE TO BE HAPPY

11:31.840 --> 11:34.000
UPTOWN FLOWER CITY

11:34.640 --> 11:35.800
Come in and feel free to look around.

11:37.280 --> 11:38.720
This is one of the rooms.

11:39.240 --> 11:40.920
Mine is the one at the far end.

11:41.640 --> 11:43.480
I saw Su Tian mention in the group chat
that you're looking for a place.

11:44.080 --> 11:45.560
It's hard to find a place
at the moment, isn't it?

11:46.200 --> 11:47.880
It's indeed hard to find a place
during the Chinese New Year.

11:47.960 --> 11:49.240
It's even harder to find a place

11:49.320 --> 11:50.520
as close to the company

11:50.600 --> 11:52.080
as mine.

11:52.600 --> 11:53.840
You can thank me later.

11:54.840 --> 11:56.200
Distance isn't a big concern for me.

11:56.280 --> 11:57.120
What I'd like to know is the rent.

11:57.200 --> 11:58.520
How can you not care about distance?

11:58.600 --> 12:00.000
In our line of work,

12:00.080 --> 12:02.080
we're always on the go,
working crazy hours.

12:02.160 --> 12:03.560
Time is money.

12:03.640 --> 12:05.760
If you can sleep longer,
why wake up earlier?

12:09.200 --> 12:10.560
This room is yours if you want it.

12:10.640 --> 12:11.760
The last tenant was a friend of mine

12:11.840 --> 12:13.400
who had moved out for a while.

12:13.480 --> 12:14.720
She dated a rich guy

12:14.800 --> 12:16.200
and upgraded to a hillside villa.

12:16.920 --> 12:17.960
Here's the bathroom.

12:19.480 --> 12:20.880
Honestly, renting with strangers

12:20.960 --> 12:22.880
these days is too risky.

12:22.960 --> 12:25.720
There are too many weirdos out there.

12:25.800 --> 12:27.080
That's why I'd rather leave it vacant

12:27.160 --> 12:28.760
than rent it to someone I don't know.

12:29.360 --> 12:31.320
That's why I offered it to you first.

12:32.400 --> 12:33.360
Take a look before you decide.

12:33.440 --> 12:35.960
Moving isn't a small thing, after all.

12:40.360 --> 12:41.840
So, that vacant room of yours…

12:44.560 --> 12:47.320
I need to take this call.
Help yourself to some water.

12:50.000 --> 12:51.160
Hello?

12:51.920 --> 12:53.200
I just wanted to ask

12:53.280 --> 12:55.240
if you got the New Year's photos.

12:56.160 --> 12:58.480
I mean the ones from our hot spring trip.

13:00.880 --> 13:02.640
Don't show them to anyone else.

13:03.400 --> 13:05.680
Don't call me that.
I'm not your girlfriend.

13:06.280 --> 13:07.120
I'm hanging up.

13:11.360 --> 13:12.680
So, what do you think?

13:12.760 --> 13:15.160
The smaller room is 3,000,
and the whole place is 7,000.

13:17.280 --> 13:19.400
We can split the utility bills equally.

13:24.440 --> 13:26.440
But if you're planning

13:26.520 --> 13:29.120
on running the AC all day,

13:29.200 --> 13:30.640
taking super long showers,

13:30.720 --> 13:33.600
and cooking daily,

13:33.680 --> 13:34.880
then we'll need a different arrangement.

13:39.560 --> 13:40.400
I'll take it then.

13:43.320 --> 13:45.280
Welcome to your new home
at Uptown Flower City.

13:47.920 --> 13:50.120
Let me know if you need anything.

14:08.040 --> 14:10.520
Although the rent here
is much higher than in Urban Haven,

14:10.600 --> 14:13.160
as long as I can get a good night's sleep,

14:13.680 --> 14:14.520
it's fine.

14:18.040 --> 14:19.240
Lin,

14:19.320 --> 14:20.840
you've already broken up with your ex.

14:20.920 --> 14:21.760
Why are you still having a meal with him?

14:21.840 --> 14:25.000
He kept begging me
to give him another chance.

14:25.080 --> 14:26.680
I know we're done,

14:26.760 --> 14:28.320
but having a meal together doesn't hurt.

14:28.960 --> 14:30.680
He even booked a fancy restaurant,

14:30.760 --> 14:32.400
so don't hesitate to dig in.

14:34.000 --> 14:34.840
Lin.

14:35.480 --> 14:38.320
Get in the car. I wasn't late.
I actually arrived half an hour ago.

14:38.920 --> 14:40.280
I just wanted to buy you a flower.

14:43.120 --> 14:44.280
Wen Yifan?

14:47.560 --> 14:49.680
You're Wen Yifan, aren't you?
I'm not mistaken this time, am I?

14:51.200 --> 14:53.040
- Are you Su Haoan?
- Yes, it's me.

14:53.680 --> 14:55.520
I ran into Zhong Siqiao
at Overtime last night

14:55.600 --> 14:56.960
and even mistook her for you.

14:59.560 --> 15:00.640
Let's talk in the car.

15:03.840 --> 15:05.040
Maybe it's better if I don't go.

15:05.120 --> 15:06.200
Why?

15:06.760 --> 15:07.680
It's fine.

15:07.760 --> 15:08.840
Let's celebrate becoming roommates.

15:10.280 --> 15:11.320
Careful.

15:13.680 --> 15:14.760
Careful.

15:14.840 --> 15:15.840
Sit tight.

15:18.160 --> 15:19.400
There's someone else.

15:29.080 --> 15:31.000
Wake up and see your romantic interest.
Wen Yifan is here.

15:35.400 --> 15:36.600
So, you all know each other?

15:37.840 --> 15:39.680
We were in the same class in high school.

15:39.760 --> 15:41.440
Romantic interest?

15:41.520 --> 15:42.400
What does that mean?

15:42.480 --> 15:44.000
Are you saying
Sang Yan had feelings for Fan

15:44.080 --> 15:45.120
but she never reciprocated?

15:46.200 --> 15:47.080
Yes.

15:47.160 --> 15:48.840
Really? How come I don't remember?

15:48.920 --> 15:50.600
Maybe you misremembered.

15:51.120 --> 15:52.440
There's no way I misremembered.

15:52.520 --> 15:54.200
Back in high school, weren't you two…?

16:00.320 --> 16:03.080
Is this awkward for you guys?

16:03.760 --> 16:04.720
It's been so many years.

16:04.800 --> 16:07.400
I was just bringing it up as a fun memory.

16:07.480 --> 16:09.560
How long has it been
since you last saw each other?

16:10.960 --> 16:11.800
Wen Yifan,

16:11.880 --> 16:14.320
I recall you transferred schools in either
your first or second year of high school.

16:15.880 --> 16:17.120
The second semester of sophomore year.

16:18.400 --> 16:19.840
So,

16:19.920 --> 16:20.960
it's been seven or eight years now.

16:21.720 --> 16:22.840
Sang Yan,

16:22.920 --> 16:24.880
why aren't you saying anything?

16:24.960 --> 16:26.200
Don't tell me you're still

16:26.280 --> 16:27.520
holding a grudge over this.

16:28.280 --> 16:29.200
He probably thinks

16:29.280 --> 16:31.200
Wen Yifan had poor taste back then
and didn't fancy him.

16:31.280 --> 16:33.040
Who knew he'd turn out just like this?

16:33.120 --> 16:34.800
Stop it. Just focus on driving.

16:42.160 --> 16:43.600
It's so late.

16:43.680 --> 16:44.960
Why are you taking so long?

16:45.040 --> 16:47.720
- Do I have to come pick you up myself?
- We were stuck in traffic.

16:47.800 --> 16:49.800
Finally, you're here.

16:50.560 --> 16:51.640
Who's that girl?

16:53.200 --> 16:54.440
Sang Yan, that's not cool.

16:54.520 --> 16:56.440
You got a girlfriend
and didn't even tell us.

16:57.040 --> 16:58.040
Quit joking around.

16:58.120 --> 17:00.080
She is our former classmate,

17:00.160 --> 17:02.320
the legendary beauty
from our high school days.

17:02.400 --> 17:03.880
No way Sang Yan
could ever be in her league.

17:07.280 --> 17:08.359
Wen Yifan,

17:08.440 --> 17:10.760
meet Qian Fei and Chen Junwen.

17:10.839 --> 17:13.280
- They were Sang Yan's dormmates.
- Hello.

17:13.359 --> 17:15.680
As for me, I'm their closest friend.

17:17.480 --> 17:19.920
The four of us run Overtime,
our gastropub, together.

17:20.839 --> 17:22.520
- Hi.
- Don't try to cozy up to her.

17:23.760 --> 17:25.520
Let's eat first. I'm starving.

17:27.040 --> 17:28.359
Let's eat. Come on.

17:32.680 --> 17:33.520
Thank you.

17:40.800 --> 17:41.640
Come on.

17:43.360 --> 17:44.600
Let's have some cold dishes first.

17:44.680 --> 17:46.560
We can treat today
like a New Year's celebration.

17:46.640 --> 17:48.480
- Okay.
- None of you were available on New Year's,

17:48.560 --> 17:50.640
so I had to run Overtime all by myself.

17:50.720 --> 17:51.640
I was working overtime.

17:51.720 --> 17:53.760
It's part of my job.
Just ask Fan if you don't believe me.

17:53.840 --> 17:55.520
I just wanted to ask

17:55.600 --> 17:57.800
if you got the New Year's photos.

17:57.880 --> 18:00.160
I mean the ones from our hot spring trip.

18:02.800 --> 18:04.800
It's okay, as long as you're here.

18:06.480 --> 18:09.520
- This is for you.
- Thanks.

18:15.920 --> 18:16.840
Since everyone's gathered here today,

18:16.920 --> 18:19.160
let's celebrate Sang Yan's birthday
together.

18:19.240 --> 18:21.240
January 2nd. A Capricorn?

18:21.320 --> 18:22.760
I'm getting emotional.

18:22.840 --> 18:24.880
Did you get my permission
to celebrate my birthday?

18:24.960 --> 18:27.080
Dude, this is a surprise.
Why aren't you showing some appreciation?

18:27.160 --> 18:28.560
Dude, you brought it up so early.

18:28.640 --> 18:29.960
How can we still call this a surprise?

18:30.040 --> 18:31.640
You know Su Haoan.

18:31.720 --> 18:32.680
He can't keep secrets.

18:32.760 --> 18:33.920
You are quite something.

18:34.000 --> 18:35.080
I'm speechless.

18:35.160 --> 18:36.480
Sorry. My bad.

18:36.560 --> 18:37.600
- Come on.
- Come on.

18:37.680 --> 18:39.400
- Happy Birthday.
- Happy Birthday.

18:46.640 --> 18:47.600
Fan,

18:47.680 --> 18:50.400
you rejected Sang Yan before?

18:51.200 --> 18:53.240
I just don't get it.

18:53.320 --> 18:54.680
He's got everything,

18:54.760 --> 18:56.480
the looks, the height, the money.

18:57.120 --> 19:00.640
But seeing how cold he is today,

19:00.720 --> 19:02.640
it's possible he doesn't have any feelings
for you anymore.

19:05.640 --> 19:06.760
It's all in the past now.

19:10.760 --> 19:13.760
You need to learn
how to seize opportunities.

19:13.840 --> 19:14.760
Sometimes,

19:14.840 --> 19:17.520
finding a good partner
can be more effective than a promotion.

19:22.200 --> 19:24.040
By the way,
what lipstick shade are you wearing?

19:24.120 --> 19:25.320
It's really nice.

19:25.400 --> 19:26.480
I didn't wear any today.

19:26.560 --> 19:27.720
Normally, I use…

19:28.480 --> 19:29.440
We are both women.

19:29.520 --> 19:31.440
Can't you just be honest?

19:37.960 --> 19:39.160
I really didn't wear any.

19:57.080 --> 19:58.240
It's been a while.

20:01.800 --> 20:03.880
It's been a while?

20:04.880 --> 20:06.840
It's only been two days
since the New Year's event.

20:07.480 --> 20:10.560
No need to act like you've been missing me
as if it's been ages.

20:13.880 --> 20:16.120
You were the one
acting like you didn't know me.

20:16.720 --> 20:18.560
I thought you didn't recognize me

20:18.640 --> 20:21.440
since I was wearing a mask that day,
covering my face completely.

20:21.520 --> 20:23.240
I didn't expect your eyes
to be that sharp.

20:23.760 --> 20:25.120
My eyes are sharp?

20:26.920 --> 20:29.120
Sorry, you got it wrong.

20:30.000 --> 20:30.840
I didn't see you at all.

20:30.920 --> 20:32.040
It was my sister who saw you

20:33.000 --> 20:34.480
and mentioned

20:34.560 --> 20:35.880
that you were staring at me.

20:38.680 --> 20:41.120
That's true. Because I noticed

20:42.160 --> 20:43.400
your zipper was down.

20:48.320 --> 20:51.280
A lot of people around me
were talking about it at the time.

20:52.320 --> 20:54.240
But don't worry too much since it has been

20:54.840 --> 20:55.960
a few hours already.

20:56.040 --> 20:57.040
I'm off now.

21:21.000 --> 21:22.560
They were talking about a limited edition
or something.

21:22.640 --> 21:24.440
Come on. Here,
let's have a toast together.

21:25.200 --> 21:26.240
Here.

21:33.480 --> 21:34.840
Any updates on the singer?

21:34.920 --> 21:36.640
A couple of friends
recommended a few to me the other day.

21:36.720 --> 21:39.600
Sorry, I need to head back now.

21:39.680 --> 21:42.360
My supervisor just told me
that I have a task to finish.

21:42.960 --> 21:44.440
- You hardly ate anything.
- Are you full?

21:44.520 --> 21:45.800
Is it because of Ms. Qian?
I'll talk to her.

21:45.880 --> 21:46.720
No need.

21:46.800 --> 21:48.440
I just passed my probation period,
if you know what I mean.

21:49.080 --> 21:50.800
- You've worked hard.
- Stay safe on your way back.

21:50.880 --> 21:52.640
- Okay.
- Bye, beauty.

21:53.560 --> 21:54.640
Why…

21:54.720 --> 21:55.800
What's wrong?

21:57.240 --> 21:58.400
Let's have a toast together.

22:17.880 --> 22:19.720
Do you still remember which floor
Su Haoan's car was parked on?

22:21.040 --> 22:23.240
I think it's on the second basement floor.
You don't remember?

22:24.160 --> 22:25.240
Which section and what number?

22:27.320 --> 22:29.200
It should be section A,

22:29.280 --> 22:30.760
at the turn.

22:32.040 --> 22:33.360
All right, lead the way.

22:45.400 --> 22:46.440
Here it is.

22:55.080 --> 22:56.080
Hey,

22:57.520 --> 22:59.200
could you give me a ride?

22:59.280 --> 23:01.120
It's really hard
to get a cab during rush hour.

23:01.200 --> 23:02.720
- Where do you live?
- Urban Haven.

23:04.240 --> 23:05.280
It's a detour for me.

23:06.160 --> 23:07.480
I won't trouble you then.

23:28.400 --> 23:30.280
56 PEOPLE AHEAD
ESTIMATED WAITING TIME IS 60 MINUTES

23:52.280 --> 23:54.240
I never said I wouldn't give you a ride
just because it's a detour.

23:55.040 --> 23:57.120
It's probably going to take
over 50 minutes for you to get a cab now.

23:58.360 --> 24:00.080
55 PEOPLE AHEAD
ESTIMATED WAITING TIME IS 58 MINUTES

24:00.160 --> 24:01.760
How come he knows?

24:01.840 --> 24:03.160
Let's go.

24:09.760 --> 24:11.520
54 PEOPLE AHEAD
ESTIMATED WAITING TIME IS 57 MINUTES

24:12.320 --> 24:13.360
Thank you.

24:15.400 --> 24:19.200
Um, you can just drop me off
at the nearest subway station.

24:19.280 --> 24:20.560
Thanks for helping me out.

24:20.640 --> 24:21.880
Such good manners.

24:41.880 --> 24:43.440
How about some music?

24:49.160 --> 24:50.680
MEDIA

24:50.760 --> 24:52.600
CHINA NATIONAL RADIO

25:02.000 --> 25:03.480
Are you not staying to eat with them?

25:03.560 --> 25:04.920
They are too noisy.

25:12.080 --> 25:14.960
- You haven't seen them in a while, right?
- Not really.

25:19.160 --> 25:20.920
It's your birthday today, right?

25:22.720 --> 25:23.680
You forgot?

25:38.680 --> 25:39.560
Do you like it?

25:41.520 --> 25:42.680
From you?

25:45.280 --> 25:46.560
What's with the sudden gift?

25:46.640 --> 25:47.720
It's for your birthday.

25:48.240 --> 25:50.600
I thought you were born
during Frost's Descent.

25:52.400 --> 25:53.960
- You remembered?
- It's easy to remember.

25:57.200 --> 25:58.040
Thank you.

26:02.440 --> 26:04.040
Does this mean

26:04.120 --> 26:06.560
I'll have to remember
your birthday from now on?

26:09.320 --> 26:10.320
Don't worry about it.

26:10.400 --> 26:11.440
I don't really celebrate my birthday.

26:17.200 --> 26:19.560
I'm a Capricorn, born on January 2nd,

26:19.640 --> 26:20.880
and I'm not really
into celebrating my birthday.

26:38.320 --> 26:39.440
We seem to have passed it.

26:42.200 --> 26:43.480
But it's all right.

26:43.560 --> 26:46.040
There's another subway entrance ahead.
Just drop me off there.

26:46.120 --> 26:47.360
Am I your driver?

26:53.400 --> 26:55.280
Where are we going then?

26:55.360 --> 26:57.360
Your home, of course.
Where else do you think we'll be going?

27:09.440 --> 27:11.080
So,

27:11.680 --> 27:14.360
when you are free next time,
I'll treat you to a meal.

27:14.440 --> 27:15.320
Thanks a lot for today.

27:16.320 --> 27:18.040
You're already planning
for our next meeting?

27:23.440 --> 27:25.240
Earlier at Overtime,

27:25.800 --> 27:27.600
I think I misspoke.

27:27.680 --> 27:29.000
What are you referring to?

27:30.240 --> 27:31.480
You mean when you said
it was a bit of a pity?

27:35.080 --> 27:36.840
Thank you. I'll go home now.

28:38.440 --> 28:39.680
Dian.

28:43.200 --> 28:44.200
Dian.

28:46.880 --> 28:48.960
- Hey, does it taste all right to you?
- It's not bad.

28:49.040 --> 28:50.640
- Good.
- Meow.

28:53.120 --> 28:54.200
Eat more.

28:59.520 --> 29:00.760
Who is it?

29:02.480 --> 29:03.800
Oh, the pretty lady.

29:03.880 --> 29:04.960
You are back.

29:05.800 --> 29:07.120
Give me back my cat.

29:08.080 --> 29:09.240
We've finally met in person.

29:09.840 --> 29:11.240
So, you're the one
who had our friends stuck

29:11.320 --> 29:13.320
at the police station for days, huh?

29:26.840 --> 29:29.320
You don't know how to maintain harmony
with the neighbors, do you?

29:29.400 --> 29:30.600
Give me back my cat.

29:30.680 --> 29:32.280
Here. Here's your cat.

29:33.520 --> 29:34.680
I think she really doesn't get it.

29:34.760 --> 29:36.600
Should we teach her a lesson?

29:37.520 --> 29:38.560
- Go away!
- Don't be afraid.

29:38.640 --> 29:39.800
Let go of me!

29:39.880 --> 29:40.720
Go away!

29:41.880 --> 29:42.960
My foot.

29:44.160 --> 29:45.120
Fuck.

29:45.200 --> 29:46.040
Go after her!

29:46.560 --> 29:47.440
Stop right there!

29:50.120 --> 29:51.200
Stop!

29:52.760 --> 29:53.600
Stop right there!

30:00.120 --> 30:01.040
Stop!

30:01.920 --> 30:03.760
- Are you all right?
- Stop!

30:06.280 --> 30:07.120
- Go after her!
- Stop!

30:07.920 --> 30:08.760
Go after her!

30:10.400 --> 30:11.760
Keep running.

30:11.840 --> 30:12.840
You were pretty fast, weren't you?

30:14.560 --> 30:16.640
Keep running then.

30:17.240 --> 30:18.440
Darn it!

30:19.200 --> 30:20.200
Who did this?

30:22.560 --> 30:24.480
Give me your hand. Your hand.

30:25.440 --> 30:26.480
Don't you dare to run away!

30:32.520 --> 30:34.400
- Get in the car.
- What about you?

30:36.640 --> 30:37.800
Watch out!

30:46.680 --> 30:47.920
Watch out, Sang Yan.

30:53.720 --> 30:54.800
Open the door!

31:01.200 --> 31:02.040
Open the door!

31:05.320 --> 31:06.640
Watch out, Sang Yan.

31:07.440 --> 31:08.640
Stop!

31:13.080 --> 31:15.320
Is this the police?
I need to file a report.

31:37.000 --> 31:38.040
Open the window.

31:41.600 --> 31:43.640
- Careful. All you all right?
- Drive.

32:02.720 --> 32:05.120
RESTRICTED OFFICE AREA
AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL ONLY

32:13.120 --> 32:15.200
Should we head to the hospital?

32:19.040 --> 32:21.120
Do you have any other injuries?

32:21.200 --> 32:22.880
- Let's go to the hospital.
- Wen Yifan.

32:26.640 --> 32:28.000
Did you not see me standing there?

32:31.160 --> 32:32.680
- What's the matter?
- Why didn't you ask me for help?

32:32.760 --> 32:33.960
Why did you run?

32:39.360 --> 32:40.240
Where did you go?

32:40.320 --> 32:41.880
Why is it taking you so long
to grab something?

32:41.960 --> 32:43.840
I'm still waiting for you to come back
and cut the cake.

32:43.920 --> 32:44.760
- Stop nagging.
- Stop!

32:44.840 --> 32:45.840
I'll be right back.

32:50.040 --> 32:51.160
Stop!

32:51.680 --> 32:52.720
Wen Yifan.

32:54.480 --> 32:55.520
Come here.

32:56.920 --> 32:58.120
Stop!

33:01.440 --> 33:02.400
I was so loud
when I told you to come over.

33:02.480 --> 33:03.400
Couldn't you hear me?

33:03.480 --> 33:04.400
You could neither hear me nor see me.

33:04.480 --> 33:05.800
You were too busy
racing against others, huh?

33:18.760 --> 33:21.200
Actually, I wanted to ask you for help,

33:21.920 --> 33:22.800
but I wasn't sure

33:22.880 --> 33:24.600
if they'd actually get physical.

33:29.840 --> 33:30.720
I didn't want to drag you into it.

33:34.560 --> 33:35.400
Besides,

33:35.920 --> 33:38.160
there were three of them.

33:38.240 --> 33:40.560
I was worried
you might not be able to handle them.

33:56.400 --> 33:58.400
Is it okay if I pull over up ahead?

33:59.880 --> 34:02.600
HEPING PHARMACY

34:04.760 --> 34:05.760
Wait for me.

34:17.000 --> 34:20.639
MEDICAL INSURANCE CARD PAYMENT

34:22.000 --> 34:23.120
Welcome to our store.

34:49.679 --> 34:51.920
- What are you doing?
- Apply some ointment.

34:53.120 --> 34:53.960
No, thanks.

34:55.920 --> 34:59.200
If you don't apply the ointment,
I'm worried you might get tetanus,

35:00.000 --> 35:01.520
and it could be fatal.

35:02.120 --> 35:04.880
I don't want to be responsible for that.

35:31.160 --> 35:32.000
Do you need a hand?

35:54.160 --> 35:55.040
Does it hurt?

35:55.920 --> 35:57.000
No.

36:15.320 --> 36:16.400
Let me apply some on your face as well.

36:24.280 --> 36:26.160
You are just applying some ointment.

36:26.240 --> 36:27.680
Is it necessary to get so close?

36:30.160 --> 36:31.200
Sorry.

36:32.560 --> 36:34.880
It's too dark,
and I'm worried that I can't see clearly.

36:48.120 --> 36:50.040
All right. Turn around.

37:17.400 --> 37:18.400
I'll do it myself.

37:45.520 --> 37:46.560
Where will you be staying tonight?

37:47.720 --> 37:50.480
I'll stay at my friend's place tonight.

37:51.080 --> 37:52.680
But I've already found a new place.

37:52.760 --> 37:54.120
I just haven't had the time to move yet.

37:59.080 --> 38:00.040
Goodbye.

39:19.880 --> 39:21.080
This is my place.

39:24.840 --> 39:25.680
Goodbye.

39:25.760 --> 39:28.120
Are you going to keep saying goodbye?

39:34.120 --> 39:36.800
- Is there anything else?
- Go in and pack your things.

39:38.640 --> 39:40.360
You're not actually planning
to come back to this dump, are you?

39:55.400 --> 39:56.400
Feel free to sit down.

39:56.480 --> 39:58.040
I'll go pack my things.

39:58.120 --> 39:59.040
No, thanks.

40:04.960 --> 40:06.480
I bet you were terrified just now.

40:35.920 --> 40:36.800
Let me ask you this.

40:37.640 --> 40:39.120
After all that has happened,

40:39.200 --> 40:40.200
why haven't you been more careful?

40:42.720 --> 40:44.880
I thought that person
was still at the police station,

40:44.960 --> 40:46.320
so I assumed it was safe
for the time being.

40:50.720 --> 40:52.000
Are these all you've got?

40:53.000 --> 40:54.320
I'm on my own.

40:54.400 --> 40:56.040
I don't have a lot of stuff.

40:56.120 --> 40:57.160
These are everything I own.

41:42.560 --> 41:43.520
We are almost there.

41:45.240 --> 41:46.600
Which building does your friend live in?

41:47.600 --> 41:49.320
I can't quite remember.

41:49.840 --> 41:51.400
I came during the day the last time.

41:53.880 --> 41:55.360
Do you really have a friend living here?

41:58.920 --> 42:01.720
I really appreciate your help today.

42:03.360 --> 42:05.560
Let me know when you're free,
and I'll treat you to a meal.

42:05.640 --> 42:06.920
Don't worry about the meal.

42:07.000 --> 42:08.920
Even if I didn't know you,

42:09.000 --> 42:10.040
I would've done the same thing today.

42:13.520 --> 42:15.320
After all the heroic acts,

42:15.840 --> 42:17.120
will your face still be presentable

42:17.640 --> 42:19.240
by the end of the year?

42:23.840 --> 42:24.880
Even if

42:24.960 --> 42:26.880
you're temporarily scarred,

42:27.400 --> 42:29.320
it doesn't take away your charm.

42:42.440 --> 42:45.000
Thanks. You can just put them here.

42:49.360 --> 42:51.040
I could have handled it on my own.

42:51.120 --> 42:52.040
UPTOWN FLOWER CITY

43:02.440 --> 43:03.320
Thank you.

43:05.600 --> 43:06.440
You can just leave them here.

43:06.520 --> 43:07.800
My roommate is a girl.

43:07.880 --> 43:09.400
I can go up myself.

43:11.000 --> 43:11.840
I'm leaving now.

43:51.960 --> 43:52.800
WEN YIFAN

43:52.880 --> 43:56.280
HAPPY NEW YEAR!
YOU DON'T HAVE TO BE HAPPY

44:01.160 --> 44:02.360
Bro.

44:02.440 --> 44:03.640
Congratulations on making it out.

44:03.720 --> 44:05.440
First, take a shower
to wash off the bad luck,

44:05.520 --> 44:07.080
then step over a fire pot.

44:07.160 --> 44:08.040
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

44:08.120 --> 44:10.800
Come on. We will drink with you
to your heart's content tonight.

44:10.880 --> 44:11.720
Here.

44:12.320 --> 44:13.680
My wife was gone,

44:13.760 --> 44:15.040
and on top of that,
I ended up in the police station.

44:15.120 --> 44:15.960
Yeah.

44:16.040 --> 44:18.440
We intended to bring her
to apologize to you a few days ago,

44:18.520 --> 44:20.280
but unfortunately, she ran away.

44:20.800 --> 44:23.040
Honestly, I should have installed a camera

44:23.120 --> 44:24.560
and filmed it all from the beginning.

44:24.640 --> 44:25.880
She doesn't want me to see it, huh?

44:25.960 --> 44:28.080
- Yes.
- I'll show it to the whole world.

44:28.160 --> 44:29.080
Exactly.

44:29.160 --> 44:30.400
- Let's drink.
- Come on, bro.

44:30.480 --> 44:31.360
You know.

44:50.920 --> 44:51.840
Wait.

44:51.920 --> 44:53.960
What's going on?

44:55.640 --> 44:57.000
I just wanted to check

44:59.240 --> 45:01.560
if they really installed hidden cameras.

45:05.160 --> 45:06.000
Hey, are you serious?

45:06.080 --> 45:07.600
Are you some kind of creep?

45:07.680 --> 45:09.800
- Cameras? Are you kidding me?
- No!

45:09.880 --> 45:11.320
What's wrong with you?

45:11.400 --> 45:12.240
Did you all

45:12.320 --> 45:14.160
see my floral boxer?

45:14.240 --> 45:16.400
- No, I just…
- You want to sell it for cash, huh?

48:00.160 --> 48:01.280
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

48:01.360 --> 48:02.400
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
